snippet.title: Parcel Corps Release Date Reveal Trailer -  Future Games Show Summer Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
Billy Goat Entertainment dropped the Release Date Trailer for Parcel Corps during this year’s Summer Showcase. The gig economy delivery driver simulator is coming to PC and consoles on September 3rd. 

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS
